original_title: UFC Fight Night 49: Henderson vs. Dos Anjos
overview: UFC Fight Night 49: Henderson vs. Dos Anjos was a mixed martial arts event held on August 23, 2014, at the BOK Center in Tulsa, Oklahoma. The event was headlined by Lightweight contenders Benson Henderson and Rafael dos Anjos.
title: UFC Fight Night 49: Henderson vs. Dos Anjos
